Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:16.49,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:02.77,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,哟西 喝点咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.14,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,虽然也不是特别的喜欢咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:08.36,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,但是我喜欢咖啡店里的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:09.68,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.63,Default,Both,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:12.24,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,噢 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:16.49,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}剧场 {\1c&H000000&} 之三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:21.40,SignC,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\fs26}{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}剧场{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HC4C700&\b1\bord6}③{\bord2}{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}主{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}人{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}和、他{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}的{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}女{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}仆们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:18.43,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,在这个情况...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.43,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你真棒 异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:23.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这才是我梦想中的女仆咖啡馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:24.75,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,雷姆雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,主人在说什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:28.13,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,大概脑子有点问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.27,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,姐姐姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,即使这样主人也是很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:35.21,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,虽然姐姐的反应让我难以接受是一个女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:38.68,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,但是 不是对罗兹亲 而是叫我主人 这种情况很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:43.03,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,主人 你能快点下单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:44.57,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我看下菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:45.93,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,拉姆的暖暖蒸红薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.02,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,和整人蒸红薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有心情无常蒸红薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.72,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,呃 你这不是只有蒸红薯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.18,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,价格不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:54.46,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,根据价格杀必死也不一样是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.72,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,毕竟是女仆咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.65,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,根据红薯的个数不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.20,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,普通 那个太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.91,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你们没有吗 女仆咖啡的杀必死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.33,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,我可以为了主人专门摆一个pose 一次500
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.99,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,就是这种就是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.02,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,500块啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这个价格也有点普通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但机会难得给我来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:15.50,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.69,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这是嘲讽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:20.29,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这种时候难道不是摆可爱的姿势吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:22.15,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,姐姐一直都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:23.42,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,雷姆小姐雷姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能成为主人的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:28.55,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,嗯 我当然是主人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.76,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,但是姐姐非常的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.74,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,那个 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:36.49,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这种时候我觉得你应该对着我才对压
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.29,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,你说没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,作为女仆不看主人的确是有一些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.15,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.61,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,那再给你特别弄一个姿势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:46.21,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你这不是在鄙视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,讲道理不应该尊敬我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.60,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,姐姐一直都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.69,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,雷姆小姐雷姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要成为顾客的伙伴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.84,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,嗯 雷姆当然是顾客的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.01,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,但是姐姐非常的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.30,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,作为女仆咖啡给我搞一些正经的杀必死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.54,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,确实是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.49,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.75,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,为了回应主人的希望 我可以给你一些女仆的杀必死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.58,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,就是要这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.03,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,那么 有什么杀必死呢 比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.31,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,比如...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.25,Default,Ram,0,0,0,,拳头碎大桌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.10,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你那不是女仆杀必死吧
